This C++ program takes a piece of ciphertext, encoded using either vigenere cipher or shift cipher, and returns the plaintext version.

### Compiling

A makefile is provided. Enter 'make' into terminal to compile project.

### Running

After compiling, enter './output cipheri.txt'. Replace i with 1, 2, 3, or 4 depending on the ciphertext to be decrypted.
